      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Plum Island Conservation Act</b> </p> <p>This bill amends the Consolidated Security, Disaster Assistance, and Continuing Appropriations Act, 2009 and the Consolidated Appropriations Act, 2012 to repeal provisions requiring the sale of federal property and assets supporting the Department of Homeland Security's Plum Island Animal Disease Center in New York. </p>]]></text>
